cheese-the-duck (2.30.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Fixed git-based local installs never being able to self-update: the
    untracked uninstall.sh created by the installer was misread as local
    changes and aborted every update
  * Added regression tests covering the git update path

 -- Cheese the Duck Team <cheese@example.com>  Wed, 10 Jun 2026 01:50:00 +0000

cheese-the-duck (2.30.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Made all quests completable: collect/find/talk objective progress now
    emitted, quest decision prompt added, prerequisite-free quests offered
  * Quest items discoverable via fishing, digging, and special weather
  * Crafted items no longer vanish: 16 recipe results plus quest tokens
    and quest rewards added to the item registry
  * Wired particle, animation, and weather effect settings to the renderer
  * Fixed '=' diary key being shadowed by volume-up; help generated from
    a single key reference table
  * Debian packages now include root-level music files (installs were silent)
  * Converted music WAVs to OGG (59MB to 5.2MB)
  * Pinned AI model download URLs with fallback; added GitHub Actions CI
  * Logged previously swallowed event bus, updater, and settings errors
  * Standardized Python 3.9 minimum across installers and packaging

 -- Cheese the Duck Team <cheese@example.com>  Wed, 10 Jun 2026 01:37:00 +0000

